cl4 is a Kohana module that enhances the built-in Kohana functionality to:

- facilitate the creation of HTML forms and form elements based on ORM models
- facilitate the creation of tables of data based on ORM models
- facilitate the creation of PDF files
- facilitate the creation of CSV files
- facilitate the sending of emails

In conjunction with the cl4_base Kohana module, you can quickly create a public/private website
that has login/logout/forgot password functionality and some full-featured database admin pages.